survived the auschwitz and buchenwald death camps said he returned 
to say goodbye to 1000 years of jewish history in poland 
they poles do not realize that by trying to show more than 
was done to help they only antagonize the jews who have suffered 
with their pain he said 
they are laundering their own history here said doris 
epstein of toronto a psychologist who works with holocaust 
survivors 
