advance in aviation because it will not pollute the atmosphere like 
conventional jet aircraft with engines that burn oilbased fuels 
and produce hydrocarbon pollutants 
vremya showed the aircrafts takeoff and landing and a segment 
of what it said was the 21minute flight the tape showed the 
refitted jet accompanied by a conventional tu154 and in the 
footage the conventional planes exhaust was black smoke while 
vremya said the tu155 emitted harmless steam 
in an interview with vremya vk orlov the chief engine 
designer of the tu155 said the engines combined aviation and 
rocket technology he said the liquid hydrogen was stored in tanks 
aboard the plane at subfreezing temperatures 
