agnew one insider said 
ultimately his peers predicted speakes will be absolved just 
as richard nixon and gary hart regained some public dignity 
quitting merrill lynch will probably hype sales of his book 
and thats fortunate for him because it may be a long time before 
he finds a job as lucrative as the one he gave up said one new 
yorkbased public relations executive speaking on condition of 
anonymity 
